rized operator on special subspaces,\nallows us to use a fixed-point argument to show the existence of special\nsolutions. Finally, we prove the uniqueness by studying exponentially decaying\nsolutions to a sequence of linearized equations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Oct 2020 16:49:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-28"}
