ance issues. These smells are generally introduced as\ndevelopers react to dependency misbehaviour and the shortcomings of the npm\necosystem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Oct 2020 19:31:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Aug 2021 20:06:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-19"}
