velocities in excess of >500km/s), that would be\nindicative of outflows. Our findings suggest that we are probing the\ninterstellar medium and associated star formation in the quasar host galaxies\nup to radii of 10kpc, whereas we find no evidence for halos or outflows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Oct 2020 10:51:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-09"}
